metadata.name: For Better Dreams #18
metadata.description:
A radiant talisman. Watchful third eye. Use as directed.

Once minted your patterns maintain their design while stretching to accommodate changes in canvas size.

There are no rarity attributes assigned to this artwork, its value is intended to be determined by viewer aesthetic alone. That aside, there are 6 possible color palettes and 7 possible background colors. 

This artwork was created using p5js and utilizes the p5.pattern library created by Taichi Sayama.

linktr.ee/lisaorthstudio
twitter: @lisaorthstudio

metadata.name: Bound #100
metadata.description:
Our journey consists of events that happen one after the other, and most of the time these are quite linear. The parts we remember and cherish often happen when we change paths. "Bound" is about letting go and being open to events that are unpredictable and thus gaining new colorfull experiences. 

This collection exists of connected rectangles on a tight grid with lines cutting their way through the patterns made with a simple algorithm.

Press s in live mode to download.

Download a higher resolution by adding to the URL:
&density=2 / &density=3 / &density=4

Lammetje November 2022

metadata.name: Monochrome Pilgrimage (to the Sun) #40
metadata.description:
Emerging from our Technicolor Winter to find a world empty of color. We set out on a collective pilgrimage to the Sun. 

All secondary royalties reserved for the minter.

metadata.name: Guiding Light / Lost in Stillness #35
metadata.description:
Sometimes one can be lost. Not knowing where to go, frozen to action, as if any movement could be fatal against the unknown.

Then it all clicks. It may be due to a new tought, or due to the words of a loved one, it may even click thanks to the beauty of a flock of birds flying against the sky.
With a clear destination and renewed courage, the once lost can now resume their journey.


---

Made in Cables.gl


Press "P" to save a 15 second .webm video

Process can be a little wonky, and unfortunately only webm support

metadata.name: Balloonz #22
metadata.description:
3d scene with animated interactive camera

Who among us did not dream of becoming a real aeronaut as a child?
An exciting experience of overcoming gravity only by heating the air!
An endless moment of flight, joy and delight!

- random number ot Balloonz 3-7;
- random arrangement of Balloonz in space;
- 20 coloring patterns;
- 4 algorithms for generating palettes, based on the HSL model;
- 9 skyboxes with different locations, weather and time of day;
- free camera - you can move, rotate, change focal length,
as you like to achieve visual pleasure!

It is recommended to look at the full screen.


[Mouse Click] - Pause/Play
[Left Mouse Button + Move] - Сamera Rotate
[Right Mouse Button + Move] - Сamera Move
[Rotate Mouse Wheel] or [Middle Mouse Button + Move] - Сamera Zoom
[+ -] - Change Сamera Focal Length

Implemented using Three JS

metadata.name: Origin-a-tions II: Formation #33
metadata.description:
Nothing stays the same as they first origin-a-ted. Things are constantly changing from one form to another. Only those who can see all these formation steps in order can really grasp the true nature of things.

Origin-a-tions is a three-parts series of generative artwork, started with Part I: Creation and continuing now with Part II: Formation, that depicts one possible variation of how things may be originating.

* * *

20 reserved pieces will be sent as gift to collectors who minted 4 or more pieces of Origin-a-tions I: Creation.

Press S to save as PNG.

Made by: yenren / twitter.com/yenrenART
Made with: JavaScript + HTML Canvas
License: LICENSE.txt

metadata.name: Elementary Cellular Emoji Automata #231
metadata.description:
Features the full set of 1761 emojis, including skin tone and gender modifiers and all flags.
Arranged using the full 256 ruleset of one-dimensional cellular automata

If “random seed” is true then the seed of the generation is randomized using Math.random() meaning that the pattern will change on regeneration.
The ruleset, emoji, colors and all other properties will remain the same.

Auto-adjusts to screen size

Compatible with as many browsers and systems as possible
